  "name": "Infestation",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "matSplInfestatio",
  "img": "icons/creatures/invertebrates/wasp-swarm-attack.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You cause a cloud of mites, fleas, and other parasites to appear momentarily on one creature you can see within range. The target must succeed on a Constitution saving throw, or it takes [[/damage 1d6 poison]] damage, has disadvantage on the next concentration check it makes before the start of its next turn, and moves 5 feet in a random direction if it can move and its speed is at least 5 feet.</p><p>Roll a d4 for the direction: 1, north; 2, south; 3, east; or 4, west. This movement does not provoke opportunity attacks, and if the direction rolled is blocked, the target does not move.</p><p><span style=\"font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:thin;scrollbar-color:var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);color:rgb(207, 210, 218);font-family:'Roboto Condensed', sans-serif;font-size:14.625px;font-style:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:2;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(37, 40, 48);text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\">Cantrip Upgrade.\u00c2\u00a0</strong></span>When you reach 5th level, the spell causes disadvantage on the next 2 concentration checks and the damage increases to [[/damage 2d6 poison]] damage. When you reach 11th level, it causes disadvantage on the next 3 concentration checks and the damage increases to [[/damage 3d6 poison]] damage. When you reach 17th level, it causes disadvantage on the next 6 concentration checks and the damage increases to [[/damage 4d6 poison]] damage.</p>",
